extends baseEmail

block content
  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;")
    | Hi #{firstName},
  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;")
    | Welcome to #{process.env.SITE_NAME}! We're glad you're here.

  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;")
    | You can now check out Sushmeela's blog or purchase her content writing services. Whatever you're here for, we're here to help.

  table.btn.btn-primary(role="presentation", border="0", cellpadding="0", cellspacing="0", style="border-collapse: separate; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%;", width="100%")
    tbody
      tr
        td(align="left", style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; padding-bottom: 15px;", valign="top")
          table(role="presentation", border="0", cellpadding="0", cellspacing="0", style="border-collapse: separate; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; width: auto;")
            tbody
              tr
                td(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; background-color: #ff3811;", valign="top", align="center", bgcolor="#ff3811")
                  a(href=`${process.env.FRONTEND_BASEURL}`, target="_blank", style="border: solid 1px #ff3811; border-radius: 5px; box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; text-transform: capitalize; background-color: #ff3811; border-color: #ff3811; color: #ffffff;")
                    | Explore Now

  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;")
    | Here’s what you can do next:

  ul(style="list-style-type: disc; margin: 0 0 0 20px;")
    li(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 10px;")
      | **Read the Blog:**
      | Check out Sushmeela's latest posts.
    li(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 10px;")
      | **Purchase a Service:**
      | Get content writing services that fit your needs.
    li(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 10px;")
      | **Stay Updated:**
      | Sign up for updates so you don’t miss anything.

  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;")
    | To get started, just
    a(href=`${process.env.FRONTEND_BASEURL}/signIn`, style="text-decoration: none; color: #ff3811;")
      | log in
    | to your account.

  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;")
    | If you have any questions, you can reach us at
    a(href=`mailto:${process.env.EMAIL_ACCOUNT}`, style="text-decoration: none; color: blue")
      | #{process.env.EMAIL_ACCOUNT}.

  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;")
    | Thanks for joining us!

  p(style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; margin: 0;")
    | The #{process.env.SITE_NAME} Team
